text: Kahara is a settlement in Nyeri County, Kenya. It is part of Mukurweini Constituency. It is connected to Karaba by the 7 kilometres long E555 road Kenya National Assembly Official Record (Hansard) - December 4, 1996 There is a Kahara Medical Clinic == References == Category:Populated places in Central Province (Kenya) Category:Nyeri County
title: Kahara
